    <p><strong>A commercial fridge for shop use in India costs anywhere from ₹12,000 for a basic chest cooler to ₹8,00,000+ for a multi-door walk-in cold room.</strong> Whether you run a bakery, sweet shop, restaurant, grocery store, or juice bar, the right refrigerator commercial unit is one of the single biggest investments you'll make — and one that directly affects food safety, product freshness, and your monthly electricity bill. This comprehensive guide covers every type of commercial fridge available in India, honest 2026 pricing across capacities, the top brands worth considering, and practical buying advice so you don't overspend or undersize.</p>

    <p>We've compiled this guide from real dealer quotes, manufacturer price lists, and feedback from hundreds of shop owners across India who have purchased through BakeDesk. Prices listed are ex-showroom/ex-factory and exclude GST (18%) unless stated otherwise.</p>

