    <h2 id="energy-efficiency">Energy Efficiency & Electricity Costs</h2>

    <p>A commercial fridge is the single biggest electricity consumer in most small to mid-sized food businesses. Understanding energy costs helps you make a smarter buying decision and protect your margins.</p>

    <h3>Typical Daily Power Consumption by Fridge Type</h3>

